body: # What? > This is the CPUG (Clojure Paris User Group) meetup's reports. > > You'll find here things we talked about during the meetup: videos links, articles, etc. # Next meetup! ## When? - Last Tuesday of every month. - So the next one is the **26/03/2013**. ## Where? - Sfeir's Offices: ```sh 192 Avenue Charles de Gaulle 92200 Neuilly-sur-Seine, France 9Th floor 01 41 38 52 00 Metro: Line 1 Pont-de-Neuilly ``` - [Google Map](https://maps.google.com/maps?f=q&source=s_q&hl=en&geocode=&q=Sfeir,+192+Avenue+Charles+de+Gaulle,+Neuilly-sur-Seine,+France&aq=0&oq=sfeir&sll=37.0625,-95.677068&sspn=57.902911,135.263672&vpsrc=6&ie=UTF8&hq=Sfeir,&hnear=192+Avenue+Charles+de+Gaulle,+92200+Neuilly-sur-Seine,+Hauts-de-Seine,+%C3%8Ele-de-France,+France&ll=48.888819,2.259235&spn=0.023816,0.066047&t=m&z=15&lci=transit_comp&cid=6418185224756557461&iwloc=A) ## How do I subscribe? - [Doodle](http://www.doodle.com/rvp8iup2zt94enxc) - See you there soon! # Previous meetups reports - [Meetup report 26 february 2013](meetup-20130226.org) - ... # License Public Domain [Lisp Logo](http://www.lisperati.com/logo.html) By Conrad Barski, M.D.
